<div class="homes-for-ukraine">
  <img src="/images/HFU-Banner.png"
       class="attachment-full size-full"
       alt="Homes for Ukraine"
       loading="lazy"
       srcset="/images/HFU-Banner.png 1400w, /images/HFU-Banner-768x274.png 768w"
       sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px">
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
      Update your registration of interest
    </h1>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Thank you again for registering your interest in becoming a sponsor for the Homes for Ukraine Scheme.</p>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Weâ€™ve been working hard to process all the registrations and need a little more information from you, to make it easier to match your offer with people coming to the UK.</p>

    <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
      Before you start
    </h1>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Make sure you have read the guidance and have a discussion with everyone in your household about how sharing your home with people fleeing Ukraine may affect them.</p>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Read more about the <%= govuk_link_to "Homes for Ukraine scheme", "#" %></p>

    <%= govuk_button_link_to "Start", "/additional-info/start/#{params["reference"]}" %>
  </div>
</div>

<h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
  I've recorded my interest, what happens now?
</h1>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">You will be kept updated. In the first phase of the scheme, sponsors will be able to bring named Ukrainians and their immediate family members to the UK. This will launch later this week, and if you have a named family or individual you wish to support you will be able to fill in a form requesting to sponsor them.</p>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Please see further <%= govuk_link_to 'FAQs', 'https://www.gov.uk/guidance/homes-for-ukraine-scheme-frequently-asked-questions' %> for those interested in becoming a sponsor.</p>
    <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Please read the <%= govuk_link_to 'privacy notice', 'https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/homes-for-ukraine-scheme-expressions-of-interest-eois-privacy-notices' %> for further information about how the data you provide will be used before you proceed with your registration.</p>
  </div>
</div>

